➜罗红建(河南)：题图：《这一路歌声》
http://www.sohu.com/a/434694070_100115135	19887
<p class="ql-align-center"><img src="http://p1.itc.cn/images01/20201127/e58ecd301f7c40b9bc25580475a8705e.jpeg" max-width="600" /></p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><strong>题图：《这一路歌声》</strong></p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><strong> 罗红建/河南</strong></p>
<p class="ql-align-center">无需绑架半卷白纱的救赎</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">可以佯装，是一双手……</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">我想，应该足够拼凑出一些瞬间</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">尽管帧序混乱不堪</p>
<p class="ql-align-center"> 尽管</p>
<p class="ql-align-center"> 间或会有，落寞指尖纠缠</p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><strong>至于哪帧开始？哪帧失去？</strong></p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><strong>就像这些静默的叶子</strong></p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><strong> 暮时</strong></p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><strong> 何必究问哪一枚先行</strong></p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><strong>又何必追溯，那些怂恿的来路</strong></p>
<p class="ql-align-center">而此刻，只需把这里铺满</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">起风的时候——</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">你听：这一路歌声……</p>
<p class="ql-align-center"> <strong> 2020/11/26</strong></p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><img src="http://p2.itc.cn/images01/20201127/de366df3850542369b6895b5aeea4b23.jpeg" max-width="600" /></p>            <div class="lookall-box">
