<p><strong>3.图片来源网络，如有侵权，请联系主编删除。</strong></p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><img src="http://p5.itc.cn/images01/20201127/99739e9407754280ac71df4c31092a62.jpeg" max-width="600" /></p>
➜广西诗人陈熠明：万里青峰玉水环
http://www.sohu.com/a/434703179_100115135	22055
<p class="ql-align-center"><img src="http://p3.itc.cn/images01/20201127/205566db42214edb8e08e2bc33082a7d.jpeg" max-width="600" /></p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><strong>万里青峰玉水环</strong></p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><strong>(1)</strong></p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><strong>七绝·万里青峰玉水环</strong></p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><strong>诗文作者·陈熠明</strong></p>
<p class="ql-align-center">天涯碧浪倚蓝湾，万里青峰玉水环。</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">绚丽丹霞飞紫凤，云边旭日照龙山。</p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><strong>(2)</strong></p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><strong>七绝·北向云霞寻远路</strong></p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><strong>诗文作者·陈熠明</strong></p>
<p class="ql-align-center">龙潮咆哮九连湾，凤影缠绵四转环。</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">北向云霞寻远路，南方水雾问高山。</p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><strong>(3)</strong></p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><strong>七绝·霞中笑日越蓝烟</strong></p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><strong>诗文作者·陈熠明</strong></p>
<p class="ql-align-center">双飞玉鹭上青天，两哮金龙下紫源。</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">涧里流声摇碧树，霞中笑日越蓝烟。</p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><strong>(4)</strong></p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><strong>七绝·岁月花开笑雪寒</strong></p>            <div class="lookall-box">
<div class="lookall-shadow"></div>
<section class="lookall">
<a href="javascript:;" class="show-all" id="showMore">
<em>展开全文</em>
</a>
</section>
</div>
<div class="hidden-content control-hide">
<p class="ql-align-center"><strong>诗文作者·陈熠明</strong></p>
<p class="ql-align-center">水韵潺潺歌向远，林中鸟语唱青山。</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">春弦此刻逢天籁，岁月花开笑雪寒。</p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><img src="http://p8.itc.cn/images01/20201127/38887cff42bc45a0a5b1dae3824c7fd4.jpeg" max-width="600" /></p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><strong>(5)</strong></p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><strong>七绝·丹霞水岸清波影</strong></p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><strong>诗文作者·陈熠明</strong></p>
<p class="ql-align-center">雾绕淙流随涧谷，湾环潺落顺江滩。</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">丹霞水岸清波影，碧树山中玉水潭。</p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><strong>(6)</strong></p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><strong>七绝·流深北海越长龙</strong></p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><strong>诗文作者·陈熠明</strong></p>
<p class="ql-align-center">丹云日上玉霞辉，紫气峰前涧水淙。</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">望远南山飞羽鹭，流深北海越长龙。</p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><strong>(7)</strong></p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><strong>七绝·青峰日照紫云丹</strong></p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><strong>诗文作者·陈熠明</strong></p>
<p class="ql-align-center">青峰日照紫云丹，碧水歌飞玉凤蓝。</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">五虎朝山千里卧，八龙逆浪万重翻。</p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><strong>(8)</strong></p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><strong>七绝·万岭丹霞紫墨含</strong></p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><strong>诗文作者·陈熠明</strong></p>
<p class="ql-align-center">巍然屹立彩虹山，万岭丹霞紫墨含。</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">影似繁花云作色，千秋梦幻在天关。</p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><img src="http://p6.itc.cn/images01/20201127/273f4c855de7426a88de0ceca17782f8.png" max-width="600" /></p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><strong>(9)</strong></p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><strong>七绝·蓝天水日映江深</strong></p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><strong>诗文作者·陈熠明</strong></p>
<p class="ql-align-center">几缕云霞流梦影，蓝天水日映江深。</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">闲飞玉鹭惊波远，柳岸撑船渡早人。</p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><strong>(10)</strong></p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><strong>七绝·烟波荡漾水聆听</strong></p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><strong>诗文作者·陈熠明</strong></p>
<p class="ql-align-center">逍遥问向草柔青，岸上双飞紫燕情。</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">隐客船边琴落韵，烟波荡漾水聆听。</p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><strong>(11)</strong></p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><strong>七绝·云边梦处有人家</strong></p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><strong>诗文作者·陈熠明</strong></p>
<p class="ql-align-center">灵峰远上有茶花，涧谷流烟向玉霞。</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">忘返来时风正笑，云边梦处有人家。</p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><strong>(12)</strong></p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><strong>七绝·冲天擎柱汉元霄</strong></p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><strong>诗文作者·陈熠明</strong></p>
<p class="ql-align-center">冲凌地上起崇高，旭日山边引路遥。</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">远看丹峰独屹立，冲天擎柱汉元霄。</p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><img src="http://p7.itc.cn/images01/20201127/5bc6a023eb2147dbbd3b4e325ab7e2d5.jpeg" max-width="600" /></p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><strong>(13)</strong></p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><strong>七绝·水复山重路又逢</strong></p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><strong>诗文作者·陈熠明</strong></p>
<p class="ql-align-center">丹阳日照紫烟生，水复山重路又逢。</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">艳美金茶香醉客，随风起步向高登。</p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><strong>(14)</strong></p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><strong>七绝·碧水流潺韵作琴</strong></p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><strong>诗文作者·陈熠明</strong></p>
<p class="ql-align-center">藤萝碧玉翠芳新，碧水流潺韵作琴。</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">荡远长风随日上，山间鸟语落弦音。</p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><strong>(15)</strong></p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><strong>七绝·山中处处是灵仙</strong></p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><strong>诗文作者·陈熠明</strong></p>
<p class="ql-align-center">逍遥梦上九重天，苦练清修几万年。</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">翠色藤萝芳影在，山中处处是灵仙。</p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><strong>(16)</strong></p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><strong>七绝·落影青峰水更明</strong></p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><strong>诗文作者·陈熠明</strong></p>
<p class="ql-align-center">蓝天广阔有红鹰，落影青峰水更明。</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">几路兰舟随浪过，惊飞岸上鹭潮听。</p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><img src="http://p5.itc.cn/images01/20201127/7369196d636a4149b95715003f1f13b2.jpeg" max-width="600" /></p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><strong>(17)</strong></p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><strong>七绝·三潮聚会五星泉</strong></p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><strong>诗文作者·陈熠明</strong></p>
<p class="ql-align-center">三潮聚会五星泉，瀑布天龙哮子渊。</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">望远青山谁向路，冲飞影落水云间。</p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><strong>(18)</strong></p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><strong>七绝·秋云万里九重天</strong></p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><strong>诗文作者·陈熠明</strong></p>
<p class="ql-align-center">秋云万里九重天，墨影清堂聚友缘。</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">日上云霞文艺秀，书舟海浪会泽渊。</p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><strong>(19)</strong></p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><strong>七绝·布镜湖中玉水清</strong></p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><strong>诗文作者·陈熠明</strong></p>
<p class="ql-align-center">布镜湖中玉水清，神龙到过笔峰亭。</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">游来忘返归潮路，雨夏荷花正美英。</p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><strong>(20)</strong></p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><strong>七绝·瑶台梦幻锦花前</strong></p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><strong>诗文作者·陈熠明</strong></p>
<p class="ql-align-center">瑶台梦幻锦花前，日影波光醉紫烟。</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">映水蓝天云色秀，开怀仲夏美荷莲。</p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><img src="http://p9.itc.cn/images01/20201127/02429e7cb87b430497da7117e6254228.png" max-width="600" /></p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><strong>(21)</strong></p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><strong>七绝·梦里生平莫等闲</strong></p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><strong>诗文作者·陈熠明</strong></p>
<p class="ql-align-center">寒修苦渡玉云边，梦里生平莫等闲。</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">正暖春风摇碧柳，凡尘锦绣看桃嫣。</p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><strong>(22)</strong></p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><strong>七绝·风摇柳绿春烟</strong></p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><strong>诗文作者·陈熠明</strong></p>
<p class="ql-align-center">高天日上彩云间，玉水盘阳自有源。</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">万里行舟波远客，风摇柳绿醉春烟。</p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><strong>(23)</strong></p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><strong>七绝·多情碧水静流深</strong></p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><strong>诗文作者·陈熠明</strong></p>
<p class="ql-align-center">嘹歌荡漾唱情真，落影花飞秀水痕。</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">几羽黄鸭闲戏近，多情碧水静流深。</p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><strong>(24)</strong></p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><strong>七绝·静远风平玉水蓝</strong></p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><strong>诗文作者·陈熠明</strong></p>
<p class="ql-align-center">平湖半外两重山，静远风平玉水蓝。</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">万里清波云落影，高天日照锦岩滩。</p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><img src="http://p8.itc.cn/images01/20201127/53991279f71445e68ead0af7f1ede8a8.jpeg" max-width="600" /></p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><strong>(25)</strong></p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><strong>七绝·山深紫气上烟台</strong></p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><strong>诗文作者·陈熠明</strong></p>
<p class="ql-align-center">云霞梦幻日边来，碧野山花玉树开。</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">聚首回眸风雨望，山深紫气上烟台。</p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><strong>(26)</strong></p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><strong>七绝·青峰日上看霞丹</strong></p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><strong>诗文作者·陈熠明</strong></p>
<p class="ql-align-center">青峰日上看霞丹，涧里淙淙玉水潺。</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">远去天涯风雨路，天南到此第一关。</p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><strong>(27)</strong></p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><strong>七绝·跃上龙门玉水都</strong></p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><strong>诗文作者·陈熠明</strong></p>
<p class="ql-align-center">日照丹霞浪海出，鲲鹏展翅越天途。</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">翻飞远去云随浪，跃上龙门玉水都。</p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><strong>(28)</strong></p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><strong>七绝·热恋缠绵玉水湾</strong></p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><strong>诗文作者·陈熠明</strong></p>
<p class="ql-align-center">日照云霞万里山。东流远上卧龙潭，</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">环腰玉带村前绕，热恋缠绵月水湾。</p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><img src="http://p7.itc.cn/images01/20201127/c3975747493d4bebad2f794c3ca73955.jpeg" max-width="600" /></p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><strong>(29)</strong></p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><strong>七绝·鹅泉碧玉自然春</strong></p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><strong>诗文作者·陈熠明</strong></p>
<p class="ql-align-center">红蝶爱海恋乾坤，百里花开梦有魂。</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">水岸缠绵烟柳色，鹅泉碧玉自然春。</p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><strong>(30)</strong></p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><strong>七绝·兰舟万里共潮天</strong></p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><strong>诗文作者·陈熠明</strong></p>
<p class="ql-align-center">苍茫梦幻水云间，淡淡青波翠柳前。</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">荡远心潮随玉鹭，兰舟万里共潮天。</p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><strong>(31)</strong></p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><strong>七绝·登高日近看霞生</strong></p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><strong>诗文作者·陈熠明</strong></p>
<p class="ql-align-center">登高日近看霞生，但愿尘缘会有逢。</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">有梦花开云岭上，山中几道遇仙翁。</p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><strong>(32)</strong></p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><strong>七绝·新来有梦话山高</strong></p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><strong>诗文作者·陈熠明</strong></p>
<p class="ql-align-center">年华少壮问风骚，世事渊深望海潮。</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">古往无涯行路远，新来有梦话山高。</p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><img src="http://p4.itc.cn/images01/20201127/e0a613d177dd457a9df97360956ff5ac.jpeg" max-width="600" /></p>
<p>▲<strong>【作者简介】：</strong>陈熠明，笔名心灵诗幻，男，1976年生，广西平果市人。爱好文学创作，曾有诗歌作品发布于多家报刊杂志和网络。时任星连文学社副社长。职业于中医，热衷于传统文化传播。诗是文笔与文笔的向往，诗是朋友与朋友的交心。诗是千难和万险的将来，诗是岁月与年华的渴望。诗是春夏和秋冬的风景，诗是父亲和母亲的嘱咐，诗是父亲和母亲的叮咛。诗是渡船与碧波的远航，诗是生命与大海的彼岸。</p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><img src="http://p0.itc.cn/images01/20201127/d5eb0d22131049f29ce7b93956cc0842.jpeg" max-width="600" /></p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><strong>❖星连文学社管理团队：</strong></p>
<p><strong>★名誉社长:</strong>叶仲录 ☆<strong>总顾问:</strong>薛依云 ☆<strong>首席顾问:</strong>欧大象 ☆<strong>执行顾问:</strong>岩心（薛莹） ☆<strong>顾问团成员:</strong>欧大象（文光）、岩心（薛莹）、石秉旺、陈文化、高原红、碧海（陈碧珍)、黄香玉 ☆<strong>社长兼总编:</strong>星连 ☆<strong>副总编:</strong>维港泊人（香港）、朱翠荣 ☆<strong>常务副社长:</strong>岩心（薛莹） ☆<strong>副社长:</strong>丁冬亮、绝尘道长、梁继权、高晓园、陈熠明、东晓 、木子 ☆<strong>艺术总监:</strong>陆廷教 ☆<strong>编委会主任:</strong>听尘居士 ☆<strong>编委会成员:</strong>孤客、黄香玉、星连、枫叶、绮雯、徐玉兰、叶仲录、薛依云、高晓园、田书芹、木子……（添加中） ☆<strong>主编:</strong>游散居士 ☆<strong>副主编:</strong>丁冬亮、闫加辉、张立标、张君霞</p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><img src="http://p2.itc.cn/images01/20201127/d5afbcbd9e6b441a8a3415c3985f5c95.jpeg" max-width="600" /></p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><img src="http://p9.itc.cn/images01/20201127/93675516d7cd45328595b27787d48417.jpeg" max-width="600" /></p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><strong>❖主编简介:</strong></p>
<p>▲笔名：星连、星连193，原名：卢链生，号游散居士，别号：中原听真，男，汉族，七零后，籍贯：广东汕尾，现居深圳。系中国诗联协会理事，中国诗词协会会员，世界汉诗协会会员，中国网络诗歌学会会员，河北采风学会会员，中原诗词研究会会员，太行诗词协会会员，认证诗人，网站签约作家。2014年受江西电台连线采访，作品散发各大网站及入选各类诗集、文集等，诗歌及其他作品曾获特等奖、一等奖、二等奖、铜奖、优秀奖各类奖项。主要结集作品有：诗集《爱情与人生》，长篇小说《漂泊》、《江湖客传》、《都市迷情之情仇恩怨》，小说集《百味人生》以及散文集等。</p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><img src="http://p3.itc.cn/images01/20201127/87a817f43ffe40f997458641dfd49a23.jpeg" max-width="600" /></p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><strong>❖郑重声明:</strong></p>
<p><strong>1.来稿必须原创作品，所有来稿投稿者文责自负，一切纠纷与本平台无关。</strong></p>
