➜北京诗人老实：说说“道与理”
http://www.sohu.com/a/434704936_100115135	22455
<p class="ql-align-center"> <strong> 说说“道与理”</strong></p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><strong>老实心语——</strong></p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><img src="http://p8.itc.cn/images01/20201127/ad7e2fd1d7954d1fa15bc5a40597dcfb.jpeg" max-width="600" /></p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><strong>读书悟道，生活名理；诗意生活，生话诗意……</strong></p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><strong>道 与 理</strong></p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><strong>文/老实</strong></p>
<p class="ql-align-center">混沌澄明融一体，澄明混沌共常伦。</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">开天惟作开心事，辟地何论划帝臣。</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">六道轮回神化鬼，千年修炼鬼成神。</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">舜尧难说真真假，盘古无言假假真。</p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><strong>［注］首联：宇宙初始，“混沌清明”融一体。</strong></p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><img src="http://p4.itc.cn/images01/20201127/26efeb552d5943bf93a3aed87044b69f.jpeg" max-width="600" /></p>            <div class="lookall-box">
<div class="lookall-shadow"></div>
